# âœ… Chrome Desktop Icon Fix (XFCE + Intel iGPU)

## Summary

This document records the **successful setup of a desktop icon on XFCE**  
that launches Google Chrome with **stable streaming settings**,  
solving the issue where:

- Chrome works correctly when launched from the terminal
- âŒ But fails or freezes when launched from a desktop icon

The final solution ensures that **desktop icon execution behaves exactly the same as terminal execution**.

